Hebei Longma Steel Pipe Manufacturing Co., Ltd is located in Xiwang New District, Mengcun County, Hebei Province. The company was founded in 2003, with a registered capital of 131.8 million, covering an area of 70,000 square meters, with a total investment of 250 million yuan. In 2006, an investment of 310 million yuan has built a new plant area and covers an area of 150,000 square meters. The company specializes in the production: large-diameter thick-walled double-sided sub-arc-seam welding steel pipe, LSAW, ERW steel pipes…
